      "factId": "hz.web.71210b454e35b25d.fact.2",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "The first aim of Metamemetics is to create a structure of principles that foster the construction and propagation of elemental ideas.",
      "tokens": [
        "first",
        "aim",
