      "factId": "hz.web.71210b454e35b25d.fact.4",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "Because people are not used to seeing elemental technologies or concepts which are powerful and immediately usable, frequent and novel encounters with GMPG efforts provoke optimism and empowerment, nevertheless reawakening criticism of complexity and a desire for simplicity.",
